message.body: Just said goodbye to tim. Which version of the fetal position is most successful? Are you at ren fair?
Oh god! Poor baby!!! I'm not at the fair... I'm just at brunch. I have to photograph the picnic operetta later - do you want to come?
YES take me anywhere. That sounds so good. Brw, Are you doing the flashmob deal?
I think I'm doing some photos for it, ha. Yeah! You'll get to meet Kevin too. It's at 4 I think...
It's at the eat street community garden ;)
Cool, maybe I'll meet you at your place and we can car pool or caravan? 345?
When are you going to mama's boy?
This Friday at 8... I have to do the photocall after.
Hey, I'm just getting some shit done... What are you up to?
Just wanted to see if you wanted to learn the choreo for what you'll be photog ing. I'm heading over there now
Have fun, dear! I'm probably going to work here for a while, but I'll catch you later
